Package: unix-utility-suite
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Shivam <shivam2931120@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/shivam2931120/unix_mini_project
Depends: bash, zenity, xdg-utils, procps, coreutils, findutils, util-linux, iproute2, sudo, systemd, gnome-terminal | x-terminal-emulator
Recommends: mpv | vlc
Description: GUI launcher for Linux system utilities
 Unix Utility Suite is a Zenity-based desktop launcher for common
 Linux utility tasks, including system information, media launching,
 file search, package updates, PDF opening, arithmetic, process
 termination, scheduling simulation, service management, and network
 throughput monitoring.
